79
00:12:22,036 --> 00:12:24,412
Hej, skloni se odatle. Briši.

80
00:12:30,734 --> 00:12:32,349
Govoriš li engleski?

81
00:12:34,788 --> 00:12:41,254
Hoću da odem u Badek.
Badek, tamo ili tamo?

82
00:12:42,698 --> 00:12:44,868
Badek, Badek, Badek.

83
00:12:47,108 --> 00:12:53,083
Badek, Badek. - Dobro,
